Uses of Class
TowerDefense.GameObjectPlus

    • Uses of GameObjectPlus in TowerDefense

      Subclasses of GameObjectPlus in TowerDefense 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  Barricade
      Barricades are objects that stand on the path to the end goal.
      class  Character
      Characters are GameObjects that represent living beings.
      class  Destructible
      Destructibles are GameObjects that can be destroyed.
      class  EffectVisual
      A visual effect.
      class  Projectile
      A projectile is an object that is thrown by a Character.
      class  Smoke
      Smoke teleports characters and is characterized by its poofiness.
      class  Tower
      Towers are meant to sit somewhere and shoot things in various ways.
      class  TowerMedic
      This tower is a medic, which means that it has the ability to heal things.
      class  TowerSpeedy
      This tower is speedy, which means that it has the ability to speed up things.
      class  Walker
      Walkers are the characters that move along the path.
      class  WalkerBasic
      This Walker is SO basic.
      class  WalkerQuick
      This Walker moves twice as fast as the Basic Walker, but has half the health.
